# 📊 GraphQL Profile Page.

This project is a **GraphQL-powered profile page** that displays user information retrieved from the **Zone01 Oujda API**.

## online site.
🔗 **[Live Site] https://peersgraph.netlify.app/

## 📌 Features
- 🔑 **Authentication**: Users can log in using their **username/password** or **email/password**.
- 📜 **GraphQL Queries**: Retrieves **user profile data**, **XP**, **level**, **peers work time**, **audits**, and more.
- 📊 **SVG-based Graphs**: Displays **statistics** (e.g., times that you worked with your peers, audit analytics).
- 📈 **Dynamic & Interactive UI**: Provides insights into user achievements.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **GraphQL** for querying specific data
- **JWT Authentication** for secure access
- **HTML / CSS / JavaScript**
- **SVG** for data visualization
- **Netlify** for hosting
